		</a>
	</div>
</header>
<style>
	.site-header {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: space-between;
		padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
		position: sticky;
		top: 0;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
		backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
		border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(var(--petal), 0.6);
		z-index: 10;
	}

	.brand a {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		text-decoration: none;
		color: rgb(var(--rosewood));
	}

	.brand span {
		display: block;
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.4em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		color: rgba(var(--ink), 0.65);
	}

	.nav-links {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1.5rem;
	}

	.nav-links a {
		color: rgba(var(--ink), 0.8);
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: 500;
		padding-bottom: 0.25rem;
		border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
	}

	.nav-links a.active {
		color: rgb(var(--rosewood));
		border-color: rgb(var(--rosewood));
	}

	.social-links {
		display: flex;
		gap: 0.75rem;
	}

	.social-links a {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.4rem;
		padding: 0.45rem 0.9rem;
		border-radius: 999px;
		border: 1px solid rgba(var(--petal), 0.8);
		text-decoration: none;
		color: rgb(var(--rosewood));
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	.social-links a span:first-child {
		font-size: 1rem;
	}

	@media (max-width: 900px) {
		.site-header {
			flex-direction: column;
			gap: 0.75rem;
		}

		.nav-links {
			flex-wrap: wrap;
			justify-content: center;
		}
	}
</style>
